ur for drawing room walls and comes in a variety of design styles, from modern to traditional. For a genuinely sumptuous impression, combine blush pink walls with gold accents and soft, fluffy textures.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/09213538\/drawing-room-wall-colour-design-blush-pink.jpg\" alt=\"Drawing room wall colour design in blush pink\" class=\"wp-image-57576\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/09213538\/drawing-room-wall-colour-design-blush-pink.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/09213538\/drawing-room-wall-colour-design-blush-pink-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/09213538\/drawing-room-wall-colour-design-blush-pink-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/09213538\/drawing-room-wall-colour-design-blush-pink-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/09213538\/drawing-room-wall-colour-design-blush-pink-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\"> Don&#8217;t shy away from using pink in your home<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Shades of Grey Wall Colour Design for Drawing Room<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Add a dash of drama and character with lighter to darker shades of grey <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/drawing-room-interiors\/drawing-room-colour-combination-ideas\/\">drawing room wall colour combination<\/a>. It is a fantastic backdrop for artwork and ornamental items. Combine it with metallic finishes and colour pops to create a visually attractive atmosphere.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-conte